<span class='tline' id='l7' data-llen='155:181'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0002', 'WYG', '000-1a' );" name="000-1a" class="pb">[000-1a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span>
<span class='tline' id='l8' data-llen='181:197'>欽定四庫全書　　　　　經部一</span>
<span class='tline' id='l9' data-llen='197:215'>　子夏易𫝊　　　　　　　易𩔖</span>
<span class='tline' id='l10' data-llen='215:221'>　　提要</span>
<span class='tline' id='l11' data-llen='221:249'>　　　　<span class='krp-note'>臣/</span>等謹案子夏易𫝊十一卷舊本題卜子夏撰</span>
<span class='tline' id='l12' data-llen='249:272'>　　　　案説易之家最古者莫若是書其偽中生偽</span>
<span class='tline' id='l13' data-llen='272:296'>　　　　至一至再而未已者亦莫若是書唐㑹要載開</span>
<span class='tline' id='l14' data-llen='296:320'>　　　　元七年詔子夏易𫝊近無習者令儒官詳定</span>
<span class='tline' id='l15' data-llen='320:345'>　　　　劉知㡬議曰漢志易有十三家而無子夏作𫝊</span>
<span class='tline' id='l16' data-llen='345:371'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0002', 'WYG', '000-1b' );" name="000-1b" class="pb">[000-1b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span>
<span class='tline' id='l17' data-llen='371:395'>　　　　者至梁阮氏七錄始有子夏易六卷或云韓嬰</span>
<span class='tline' id='l18' data-llen='395:419'>　　　　作或云丁寛作然據漢書韓易十二篇丁易八</span>
<span class='tline' id='l19' data-llen='419:443'>　　　　篇求其符合事殊隳刺必欲行用深以為疑司</span>
<span class='tline' id='l20' data-llen='443:468'>　　　　馬貞議亦曰按劉向七畧有子夏易𫝊但此書</span>
<span class='tline' id='l21' data-llen='468:492'>　　　　不行已乆今所存多失真本荀朂中經簿云子</span>
<span class='tline' id='l22' data-llen='492:517'>　　　　夏𫝊四卷或云丁寛是先逹疑非子夏矣又隋</span>
<span class='tline' id='l23' data-llen='517:541'>　　　　書經籍志云子夏𫝊殘缺梁六卷今二卷知</span>
<span class='tline' id='l24' data-llen='541:564'>　　　　其書錯謬多矣又王儉七志引劉向七畧云</span>
<span class='tline' id='l25' data-llen='564:590'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0002', 'WYG', '000-2a' );" name="000-2a" class="pb">[000-2a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span>
<span class='tline' id='l26' data-llen='590:614'>　　　　易𫝊子夏韓氏嬰也今題不稱韓氏而載薛</span>
<span class='tline' id='l27' data-llen='614:637'>　　　　虞記其質麤畧㫖趣非逺無益後學云云是</span>
<span class='tline' id='l28' data-llen='637:662'>　　　　唐已前所謂子夏𫝊已為偽本晁説之𫝊易</span>
<span class='tline' id='l29' data-llen='662:686'>　　　　堂記又稱今號為子夏𫝊者乃唐張弧之易</span>
<span class='tline' id='l30' data-llen='686:720'>　　　　<span class='krp-note'>案唐張弧為大理寺評/事有素履子别著録</span>是唐時又一偽本並</span>
<span class='tline' id='l31' data-llen='720:744'>　　　　行故宋國史志以假託子夏易𫝊與真子夏</span>
<span class='tline' id='l32' data-llen='744:768'>　　　　易𫝊兩列其目而崇文總目亦稱此書篇第</span>
<span class='tline' id='l33' data-llen='768:791'>　　　　畧依王氏決非卜子夏之文也朱彝尊經義</span>
<span class='tline' id='l34' data-llen='791:817'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0002', 'WYG', '000-2b' );" name="000-2b" class="pb">[000-2b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span>
<span class='tline' id='l35' data-llen='817:840'>　　　　考證以陸徳明經典釋文李鼎祚周易集解</span>
<span class='tline' id='l36' data-llen='840:863'>　　　　王應麟困學記聞所引皆今本所無徳明鼎</span>
<span class='tline' id='l37' data-llen='863:886'>　　　　祚猶曰在張弧以前應麟乃南宋末人何以</span>
<span class='tline' id='l38' data-llen='886:909'>　　　　當日所見與今本乂異然則今本又出偽託</span>
<span class='tline' id='l39' data-llen='909:933'>　　　　不但非子夏書亦並非張弧書矣流𫝊既久</span>
<span class='tline' id='l40' data-llen='933:956'>　　　　姑存以備一家云爾乾隆四十五年二月恭</span>
<span class='tline' id='l41' data-llen='956:964'>　　　　校上</span>
<span class='tline' id='l42' data-llen='964:996'>　　　　　　　總纂官<span class='krp-note'>臣/</span>紀昀<span class='krp-note'>臣/</span>陸錫熊<span class='krp-note'>臣/</span>孫士毅</span>
